content: I'm bummed that I can't exclude commercial lines from the tests and exams. I don't need commercial lines and it's throwing me off.
This app helps me before taking the online quiz. Love it.
The app is okay, but it's only good as a refresher because it only ask the same 100 questions.
Very helpful tool. Highly recommended.
It is a great tool for preparing and staying abreast of vital information over time.
So much info. Really keeps you on your toes
App is awsome! Helping me alot

Nothing in the app but practice exams??? I thought the flashcards and the ListenUp.mp3 would be on it..that would make it worth the $5.00! I can get the practice exam online....I wanted more "mobile" applications when I am not in the office or don't have a laptop handy ti study with! ðŸ˜¢ðŸ˜ž disheartening....
I have personally found it very helpful. This app as of this review only has practice quizzes and practice exams. But as I said I personally find it very helpful.
Great tool to spiral in previous maerial learned

Completely disappointed in this app. I assumed this would be just like taking my pre licensing course online but instead it has the most pathetic non user friendly main menu with 4 options to practice exams and quizzes that are not even remotely as in depth as the online version. I want my god damn money back and i want it now. I will be making a report to the BBB. This is pathetic.
Very helpful
Great prep for the actual online course! Grateful to have it.
Works great

This was a great app as far as reviewing, testing your knowledge and learning more. In my experience, the questions on my exam were easier than this app. However, i did like how this app has more definitions for something as opposed to my P&C book. I dont think it's mandatory to buy this app, especially if your testing people provide you with an outline of what they will be testing you on (like how i was provided with). Good luck everyone!
None of this information is on the actual test
i really appreciate this app its extremely helpful ðŸ˜š
App is very helpful when on the go!
Pretty helpful. This alone isn't quite enough, but it's easy to study on my phone this way, and I like how it tells you whether or not you got it right right then, and explains the correct answer.
One of the best pre-testing tools!
helping me in addition to the online
I'm learning
very good
App is easy to use and the questions are very helpful.
EXAMFX DOES NOT PREPARE YOU FOR STATE EXAMS PERIOD. This company helps you pass the pre licensing requirements and lays a foundatiom for the state exams, nothing more.
Questios are always the same but are helpful for the test.
needs interchangeable questions.

I used the actual online Exam fx provided to me by my Employer. I studied and studied and much as i could i retook the test 3 times The first 2 i failed.. and passed by the 3rd thanks to this app!! i installed this app and Believe it or not It helped me Tremendously. I love the fact that on the practice exam it shows you why you got it wrong. Only downside is the questions do not change. but rate 4 out of 5
Its iight but will tell anyone & everyone out there not to soley rely just on this app to study for the exam
It's a great app
I hope this stuff is on exam
I feel with all the other tools that I'm using that this is an extra added benefit to my studying
Believe it or not, this helped tremendously. I took the quizzes a few times as well as the tests. Some of the questions are exactly the same as the real test. Passed today...1st attempt
The app needs to be electronically faced to interchange with new questions daily and or each time it is used in order to progress in a learning experience environment
I feel confident that I will be able to pass the exam by using this app.
Too repeditive
Definitely worth the price. I could quickly get through tests on short breaks and being able to review my scores was helpful. Took the real exam today and passed!
The app should sync to the active account online so it can allow me to focus on what areas of study I need to pay more attention to. Waste of money.

Silly app. What a waste. The questions never change. How are you supposed to learn anything other than these questions. The Examfx website has way more difficult questions that are not addressed with this app.
I like this app. I take this exam in 2 weeks but I already paid for the health and life app like this and it helped me pass on the first try.
It helped!  I purchased this about a week or 2 before my test and it was nice to quiz myself on questions I hadn't seen yet.  Passed first time so I think it  worked
Questions never change.
Woo hop
It helps along with the online study assessments from this same company.  I am also glad I got the paper study guide to make additional notes upon!
As everyone says the questions remain the same, would like some change in the content. Overall, this is great to use on the road, definitely use with the desktop version.
Need new questions

I had taken a class Two months ago and needed a inexpensive refresher. This app gives About 300 hundred questions to study and these questions give the full concept. I've taken the test and have my property and Casualty license, So I will being going to take the Adjusters licensing Exam. So this App is GreaT. 5.00 well spent!!!;-)
This app was a very helpful piece of my journey of becoming a licensed agent. Very thankful
Wish there was different questions each time you took the test.  That would be more helpful.
Going into my state exam More confident because I paid for this App!
Informative and easy but still need to read the content given in order to pass your exam. This app definitely helps and I enjoyed it, but again, MUST read other material in order to pass exam.
Good to freshen up before exam
Very helpful in quizzing. Questions are challenging. Would recommend
The questions never change so you are not learning anything new!
Questions in each category is limited to 10. The questions never change.
